"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/387919","Department for Work and Pensions","false","2015-07-14","<p /> <p>The information requested is not readily available, and could only be provided at disproportionate cost.</p>","Witham","Priti Patel",,"2015-07-14T14:13:11.037Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/387919/answer","Biography information for Priti Patel","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/387919/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/387919/answer",,,,,"29","Work and Pensions","Work and Pensions","2015-07-06","Jobseeker's Allowance","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Work and Pensions, how many people who were claiming income support moved to jobseeker's allowance in (a) Scotland and (b) the UK in each month since August 2014.","false","Biography information for Stuart Blair Donaldson","West Aberdeenshire and Kincardine","Stuart Blair Donaldson","5748"
