"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/386960","HM Treasury","false","2015-07-06","<p>Her Majesty’s Revenue and Customs publishes regular performance reports, which are available on <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/business-plan-indicators" target="_blank">Gov.uk.</a></p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p>","South West Hertfordshire","Mr David Gauke","5212","2015-07-06T15:47:16.703Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/386960/answer","Biography information for Mr David Gauke","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/386960/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/386960/answer",,,,,"14","Treasury","Treasury","2015-07-01","Revenue and Customs: Telephone Services","1","House of Commons","To ask Mr Chancellor of the Exchequer, what proportion of calls to the HM Revenue and Customs self assessment helpline were abandoned without answer in each of the last three years; and what the median waiting time was for such abandoned calls.","false","Biography information for Debbie Abrahams","Oldham East and Saddleworth","Debbie Abrahams","5213"
